	<text xml:lang="de">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuas accepi, chare frater, 19. octobris datas.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego quidem per dei gratiam obambulo et officia mea expedio, sed sentio totius corporis debilitatem gravem, quam et ipsam dominus potest, si vult, tollere et iustis me viribus instruere.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Negotia alioqui multiplicantur, cum interim et aetas ingravescat.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Verum iuvante et favente domino omnia sunt felicia, ac gaudeo me illi posse in extremum usque spiritum inservire.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quae sparguntur de <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispanis</placeName>, si vera sunt, a deo sunt ad cohercendam insolentiam illius petulantissimi populi; si vana, confinguntur ab illis ad practicas suas ornandas.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Es sollend 23 fendli zogen sin durch <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2765">S. Imers</placeName> taal by <placeName ref="l49" cert="high">Byel</placeName> und uff <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basel</placeName>, andere sagend uff Montpelgart<note type="margin">a.R.: ... Momp...</note> kummen sin; sol ein schön, wolgerüst <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">französisch</placeName> volck sin.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Ettlich sagend, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20348" cert="high">Conde</persName> hab sy bescheyden zum <persName type="citizen_name">printzen von Uranien</persName>; die andern sagend, sy werdint warten by <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l327" cert="high">Montpelgart</placeName><note type="margin">a.R.: ... Montp.!</note> uff hertzog <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18405" cert="high">Wolffgangen von Zweybrüggen</persName>, Pfaltzgraffen, welcher 6000 rütter und 3 regiment lantzknächt zuͦ inen bringen und mitt einandren in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Franckrych</placeName> ziehen söllend.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Weiß nitt, welches waar.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Der hertzog <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18405" cert="high">Wolffgang</persName> ist sunst gwüß in grosser rüstung für den <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20348" cert="high">Conde</persName>.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Ettlich aber sagend, die <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Franzosen</placeName> zühind von <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basel</placeName> uff[s] margraven land, danen uff die <placeName type="auto_name">Pfaltz</placeName> und zum züg des von <placeName type="auto_name">Uranien</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Da söllend enet der Maaß zwüschen <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1329" cert="high">Lüttych</placeName><note type="margin">a.R.: <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1329" cert="high">Lüttchy</placeName>!</note> und <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1772" cert="high">Maßtricht</placeName> beid heerzüg nitt wyt von einandren ligen.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="de" type="auto">So söllend die <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Engellender</placeName> uff dem meer sin mitt aller macht, alls man acht, wider den könig uff <placeName type="citizen_name">Calles</placeName> etc.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Wie ettlich <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l862" cert="high">eydgnossen</placeName> zogen zur erfollung der fendli in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Franckrych</placeName>, söllend die fürziehenden <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Franzosen</placeName> usser<note type="margin">a.R.: usset?...</note> Nüwenburg an sy kummen sin und ettlich gefertigt haben, und gadt die sag, houptman <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18022">Tugginer</persName> sye ouch wund.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Weiß nitt, [ob]s also.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Gott mitt üch.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Min herren und <placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernn</placeName> halltend an mitt grossem ernst, das die iren daheym blybind.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Datum 22. octobris 1568.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Saluta amicos nostro[s].</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus, qui semper.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ocyssime.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ornatissimo viro d. <persName ref="p8016" cert="high">Tobiae Eglio</persName>, <placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Curiensis</placeName> ecclesiae ministro fideli, domino meo colendo et charissimo fratri.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l98" cert="high">Chur</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
